commitResults.messageTitle: Added the ability to mark and unmark items in the list
commitResults.messageBody:
commands added:
- mark [index]: mark the item with index number [index] as done
- unmark [index]: mark the item with index number [index] as not done

commitResults.messageTitle: Implemented Deadline, Event and ToDo functionalities. Made deadline, event and todo classes inherit from Task class for better organisation.
commitResults.messageBody:
commands added:
- todo [item]: adds an todo item to the item list
- deadline [item] /by [date]: add a deadline item to the list
- event [item] /from [date] /to [date]: add an event item to the list
